&lt;p&gt;Wrightington Wigan and Leigh NHS Foundation Trust is a major acute trust. The Trust is dedicated to providing the best possible healthcare for the local population and surrounding areas. We aim to continuously provide safe, quality patient care to ill patients. Over 220 million is spent each year on a diverse range of reputable general and specialist acute services.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Recently voted Provider Trust of the Year at the recent HSJ Awards, Wrightington Wigan and Leigh NHS Foundation Trust is innovative, and forward thinking. The most recent initiatives ‘Christies at Wigan’ and investment into the award winning Diagnostics and Treatment Centre at Leigh Infirmary, means you will be joining a Foundation Trust at its most exciting and energetic best.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Do you wish for a career in Emergency Medicine? This is an exciting opportunity that has seen real results for post holders.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Come join us in one of the busiest Emergency Departments in Greater Manchester.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Trauma meetings and SPA time is built in to the rota.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Salary for this post will be on the Specialty Doctor pay scale, WWL are also offering a recruitment premia over the first three years in post based on basic salary as follows:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;30% in the first year.&lt;br /&gt;20% in the second year.&lt;br /&gt;10% in the third year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note, candidates will be required to present original certificates at interview.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;For overseas candidates wishing to apply for the job role and require immigration sponsorship, you can self-assess the likelihood of obtaining a CoS for the post on the &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;GOV.UK website.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;An Enhanced DBS with Children and Adult&#39;s barred lists will be completed for the successful candidate.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Muhammad Saleem Nasir&lt;/p&gt;
